title: Zoidberg in the gym
author: snatchingsouls
comment: I 100% understand Zoidberg's anger towards the less weight comment.
"Maybe you can do more reps with less weight." Epic fitness line.

"Mommy, what was my birth like?"
"Well, I was at the gym, and this crab monster said he was a doctor."

Trainer: Is there a doctor in the gym?!

Zoidberg: I'M A DOCTOR!
apperantly that is the most efffective non painful way to give birth .... ok someone lend me a zoidberg costume and a really good one
description: Episode: Futurama - 02.05 - Why Must I Be A Crustacean In Love
